Hello! I'm RunStrong AI, your running coach. I'm excited to help you reach your goals! 

It looks like we're starting fresh - I don't have any files about your training yet. To get started, I'd love to learn about:

- Your current running experience and fitness level
- What goals you're working toward (race, distance, time, etc.)
- Any injuries or areas you'd like to focus on
- Your typical weekly schedule and availability

What would you like to work on today?
